thread.title_full: Extra Space Storage reviewed by Betty Hibbert

author: Betty Hibbert
title: Betty Hibbert
text: After being robbed at Central self storage Fairfield, Rochelle was able to get me into a new storage with the camera right above the door! She knows her job, and keeps everything in clean working order!! It's a bit more expensive,but worth the peace of mind!
